{
  "stem": "1132.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, in span of about three months, they took thousands of them away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And any of the documentaries that exist attest to this, because they were just emptied out-- the small towns, the Jewish population of the small town.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that being in the large city in many ways was a protection.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course it didn't mean that you were protected completely, but it certainly was a protection.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember hearing lots of talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember hearing hush-hush as to what was going on in the countryside and in the smaller cities.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, I do remember discussions of those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, I also remember discussions of what was taking place in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how they were rounding people up, and how they were getting rid of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I have a pretty strong recollection of-- of the fear and of the knowledge that you didn't know what was going to happen to you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think that is the major point that one wants to make-- that fear in hiding can do strange things to people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I first saw Anne Frank-- the hiding in that small place up in the attic seemed extremely familiar to me with the families forced in together.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Except the point of time that I remember, things-- the last place where we were hiding, things were really not as quote, 'pleasant,' as they seemed in the 'Diary of Anne Frank' play.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, the diary itself-- the book is a whole other story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Very little furnishing in the-- in this room that I recall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I recall being on the floor on blankets and spending an awful lot of time on the floor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's-- that's parquet floor is what the recollection is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No carpeting.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
